Color::Mix version 0.02
=======================

Color::Mix is a lightweight color scheme generator for Perl.

This module allows you to generate a variety of different type
color schemes Complementary, Double Complementary, Trinary
and Analogous.

The module can be used with hexadecimal RGB color codes or
alternatively valid color names from the X11 color list.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:
 
  Test::More
  Test::Warn

